                <note rend="inline" type="source">882.124A/39: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Minister in Liberia</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Francis</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1929-07-13T13:00:00-04:00"
                            >July 13, 1929—1 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>18. Your 34, July 12, 10 a.m. Department is communicating with Rockefeller
                    Foundation and further instructions will be sent you shortly. However, if it
                    should seem to you desirable, you are still authorized in your discretion to act
                    upon Department’s 15, July 9, 5 p.m.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Stimson</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
